{"tid":1653753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡錫進：「還是會來香港旅遊、遊玩，又是一家人一樣。」","createTime":"2019-10-14T08:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:05:10.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c51e71c01be60ecf99c29ff650eb12e078e97f86","tid":1653753,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"內地官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫再度訪港，他認為反修例風波正處於十字路口，局勢有緩和跡象，但擔心部分人採取更激進手段，令局勢更難軟著陸。他又認為內地人並非仇視香港，局勢緩和後便會繼續來港旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n「香港畢竟是中國的土地，咱們畢竟是一家人，咱們血濃於水，家長和兄弟姊妹，對家裡一個出事、鬧事的孩子，也會很生氣，罵的，但畢竟是親的。只要香港局勢緩和了，大家很快把它忘掉了，還是會來香港旅遊、遊玩，又是一家人一樣。」"},{"pid":"8cf1f6f8f8fd61f8820bb02b442b03cfd389935f","tid":1653753,"uid":146074,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"屌邊撚度親"},{"pid":"ea5617e2cec3e7d1ef1fdb6097f529874dd583c7","tid":1653753,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"亲"},{"pid":"b0ef4cac1fe327075398bc1ef4a884f1bda778ab","tid":1653753,"uid":301989,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦蝗蟲 我哋係人你係蟲 一乜撚野家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3b36f943d53ec6029d0c66b5755c9977a4eac5","tid":1653753,"uid":88517,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"邊個同你有親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7238c2b46e72605da848611be5456d87c90c7b33","tid":1653753,"uid":4139,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"放心 唔會有呢一日 屌你老母"},{"pid":"5acf5320ac806e19bafdda6cff92fc91ecaef4b1","tid":1653753,"uid":309033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"家你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753119afe5e6d4e26ce33f9a27f5ccf0f04e89f1","tid":1653753,"uid":278431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:39:48.000Z"